		"description": "<p>All druids are taught to commune with nature, to become a conduit for natural power, and to maintain the secrets of their druid circle. Also at 1st level, you gain proficiency with Nature, and you learn the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.5o1rvwzxmsh5ji9i]{Druidcraft} cantrip (this does not count against your total cantrips known).&nbsp;</p>\n<p>You know Druidic, the secret language of druids. You can speak the language and use it to leave hidden messages. You and others who know this language automatically spot such a message. Others spot the message&rsquo;s presence with a successful DC 15 Wisdom (Perception) check but can&rsquo;t decipher it without magic.</p>",
